### **Question A (14 Marks)** — `[KTU University Exam - Dec 2024]`

**a)** Explain the different forms of `if` selection statements in JavaScript with syntax and examples. **(7 marks)**

**b)** Write a JavaScript program using `if...else if` to assign grades based on marks:
